{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/gulp.js/gulp---uglify를-이용하여-babel로-컴파일된-javascript-파일-축소하기/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Dryad","author":"dryad","siteUrl":"https://dryadsoft.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"dryadsoft/dryadsoft.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"jbee"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"2d06e4e6-e8b5-5532-9760-29375fe9afc3","excerpt":"목차 gulp - babel을 이용하여 개발 환경설정 gulp - javascript를 babel을 이용하여 컴파일하기 2-1. gulp - uglify를 이용하여 babel로 컴파일된 javascript 파일 축소하기 필요한 node 모듈을 설치한다. gulpfile.babel.js 파일을 수정한다. gulp 실행 컴파일된 소스 확인하기 node 실행하기 gulp - node + typescript 컴파일하기 node 프로젝트를 babel로 컴파일 후 파일 사이즈를 줄이기 위하여 gulp…","html":"<h3 id=\"목차\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AA%A9%EC%B0%A8\" aria-label=\"목차 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\">true</a>목차</h3>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"../gulp/1\">gulp - babel을 이용하여 개발 환경설정</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"../gulp/9\">gulp - javascript를 babel을 이용하여 컴파일하기</a></p>\n<p>2-1. gulp - uglify를 이용하여 babel로 컴파일된 javascript 파일 축소하기</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%ED%95%84%EC%9A%94%ED%95%9C-node-%EB%AA%A8%EB%93%88%EC%9D%84-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98%ED%95%9C%EB%8B%A4.\">필요한 node 모듈을 설치한다.</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#gulpfile.babel.js-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC%EC%9D%84-%EC%88%98%EC%A0%95%ED%95%9C%EB%8B%A4.\">gulpfile.babel.js 파일을 수정한다.</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#gulp-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89\">gulp 실행</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%BB%B4%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC%EB%90%9C-%EC%86%8C%EC%8A%A4-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">컴파일된 소스 확인하기</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#node-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">node 실행하기</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"../gulp/10\">gulp - node + typescript 컴파일하기</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>node 프로젝트를 babel로 컴파일 후 파일 사이즈를 줄이기 위하여 <strong>gulp-uglify</strong> 를 이용하여 축소 할 수 있다.\n이전 node 프로젝트의 연속포스트 이기때문에 앞부분을 보지 못했다면 먼저 보고 오길 추천한다.</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"../gulp/9\">이전포스트로 이동</a></strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"div-id필요한-node-모듈을-설치한다필요한-node-모듈을-설치한다div\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#div-id%ED%95%84%EC%9A%94%ED%95%9C-node-%EB%AA%A8%EB%93%88%EC%9D%84-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98%ED%95%9C%EB%8B%A4%ED%95%84%EC%9A%94%ED%95%9C-node-%EB%AA%A8%EB%93%88%EC%9D%84-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98%ED%95%9C%EB%8B%A4div\" aria-label=\"div id필요한 node 모듈을 설치한다필요한 node 모듈을 설치한다div permalink\" class=\"anchor before\">true</a><div id=\"필요한-node-모듈을-설치한다.\">필요한 node 모듈을 설치한다.</div></h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> <span class=\"token function\">add</span> gulp-uglify -D</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"div-idgulpfilebabeljs-파일을-수정한다gulpfilebabeljs-파일을-수정한다div\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#div-idgulpfilebabeljs-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC%EC%9D%84-%EC%88%98%EC%A0%95%ED%95%9C%EB%8B%A4gulpfilebabeljs-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC%EC%9D%84-%EC%88%98%EC%A0%95%ED%95%9C%EB%8B%A4div\" aria-label=\"div idgulpfilebabeljs 파일을 수정한다gulpfilebabeljs 파일을 수정한다div permalink\" class=\"anchor before\">true</a><div id=\"gulpfile.babel.js-파일을-수정한다.\">gulpfile.babel.js 파일을 수정한다.</div></h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> gulp <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'gulp'</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> babel <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'gulp-babel'</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> GulpUglify <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'gulp-uglify'</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// ------> uglify 추가</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> routes <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  js<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    src<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'src/**/*.js'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 대상 javascript파일</span>\n    dest<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'build'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// javascript파일이 컴파일되어서 생성되는 폴더</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">js</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span>\n  gulp\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">src</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>routes<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>js<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>src<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 출발지</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">pipe</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">babel</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// babel을 이용하여 컴파일</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">pipe</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">GulpUglify</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// ------> uglify 추가</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">pipe</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>gulp<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">dest</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>routes<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>js<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>dest<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 목적지</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> dev <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> gulp<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">series</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>js<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// package.json의 scripts에 작성한 \"gulp dev\" task</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"div-idgulp-실행gulp-실행div\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#div-idgulp-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89gulp-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89div\" aria-label=\"div idgulp 실행gulp 실행div permalink\" class=\"anchor before\">true</a><div id=\"gulp-실행\">gulp 실행</div></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>gulp를 실행하면 아래와같이 정상적으로 실행된걸 확인 할 수 있다.</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ <span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> dev\n<span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> run v1.21.0\n$ gulp dev\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>07:14:43<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> Requiring external module @babel/register\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>07:14:44<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> Using gulpfile D:<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>workspace<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>dryadsoft<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>gulp<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>gulp_javascript<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>gulpfile.babel.js\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>07:14:44<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> Starting <span class=\"token string\">'dev'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">..</span>.\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>07:14:44<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> Starting <span class=\"token string\">'js'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">..</span>.\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>07:14:45<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> Finished <span class=\"token string\">'js'</span> after <span class=\"token number\">104</span> ms\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>07:14:45<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> Finished <span class=\"token string\">'dev'</span> after <span class=\"token number\">110</span> ms\nDone <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>.85s.</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>실행결과 root디렉토리에 build 폴더가 생성된다.<br/>\n생성된build 폴더 안의 구조는 src폴더의 구조와 똑같다.<br/>\nbuild 폴더 안에 컴파일된 소스를 확인 할 수 있다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"div-id컴파일된-소스-확인하기컴파일된-소스-확인하기div\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#div-id%EC%BB%B4%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC%EB%90%9C-%EC%86%8C%EC%8A%A4-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0%EC%BB%B4%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC%EB%90%9C-%EC%86%8C%EC%8A%A4-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0div\" aria-label=\"div id컴파일된 소스 확인하기컴파일된 소스 확인하기div permalink\" class=\"anchor before\">true</a><div id=\"컴파일된-소스-확인하기\">컴파일된 소스 확인하기</div></h2>\n<p>build폴더를 확인하면 아래와 같이 소스가 축소 되어 있는 걸 확인 할 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// build/index.js</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">'use strict'</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> _utils <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'./components/utils'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> _utils<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>plus<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// build/components/utils.js</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'use strict'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nObject<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">defineProperty</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>exports<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'__esModule'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> value<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>exports<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>plus <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">plus</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> s</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> s<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\nexports<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>plus <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> plus</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"div-idnode-실행하기node-실행하기div\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#div-idnode-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0node-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0div\" aria-label=\"div idnode 실행하기node 실행하기div permalink\" class=\"anchor before\">true</a><div id=\"node-실행하기\">node 실행하기</div></h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ node build/index.js\n<span class=\"token number\">9</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>컴파일된 js파일을 실행하면 위와 같이 정상적으로 실행된 결과값을 확인 할 수 있다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"목차-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AA%A9%EC%B0%A8-1\" aria-label=\"목차 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\">true</a>목차</h3>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"../gulp/1\">gulp - babel을 이용하여 개발 환경설정</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"../gulp/9\">gulp - javascript를 babel을 이용하여 컴파일하기</a></p>\n<p>2-1. gulp - uglify를 이용하여 babel로 컴파일된 javascript 파일 축소하기</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%ED%95%84%EC%9A%94%ED%95%9C-node-%EB%AA%A8%EB%93%88%EC%9D%84-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98%ED%95%9C%EB%8B%A4.\">필요한 node 모듈을 설치한다.</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#gulpfile.babel.js-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC%EC%9D%84-%EC%88%98%EC%A0%95%ED%95%9C%EB%8B%A4.\">gulpfile.babel.js 파일을 수정한다.</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#gulp-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89\">gulp 실행</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%BB%B4%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC%EB%90%9C-%EC%86%8C%EC%8A%A4-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">컴파일된 소스 확인하기</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#node-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">node 실행하기</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"../gulp/10\">gulp - node + typescript 컴파일하기</a></li>\n</ol>","frontmatter":{"title":"gulp - uglify를 이용하여 babel로 컴파일된 javascript 파일 축소하기","date":"November 08, 2020"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/gulp.js/gulp---uglify를-이용하여-babel로-컴파일된-javascript-파일-축소하기/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/git/git-오류-해결방법/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"git 오류 해결방법","category":"git","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/react-native/react-native-apk사이즈-줄이기/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"React Native apk사이즈 줄이기","category":"react-native","draft":false}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3128451518","521680639"]}